Package: freedomhouse
Title: Version en Castellano de los Datos de 'Freedom House's Freedom in
    the World'
Version: 0.2
Authors@R:
    person("Mauricio", "Vargas", , "m.sepulveda@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1017-7574"))
Description: Desde 1973, Freedom House evalúa la situación de los derechos
    políticos y las libertades civiles en todo el mundo. La utilizan
    regularmente responsables de la formulación de políticas, periodistas,
    académicos, activistas y muchos otros. Este paquete facilita el uso de
    los datos de Freedom House's Freedom in the World en R.  English:
    Since 1973, Freedom House has assessed the condition of political
    rights and civil liberties around the world. It is used on a regular
    basis by policymakers, journalists, academics, activists, and many
    others. This package makes it easier to use the Freedom House's
    Freedom in the World data within R.
